summary: I  LOVE  HALLOWEEN I changed costumes. I’m on my second of the day now. And I love them both with my whole heart.  So all day at...
body:
I 

LOVE 

HALLOWEEN

I changed costumes. I’m on my second of the day now. And I love them both with my whole heart. 

So all day at school I was dressed as Spider Man at the end of Infinity War (dressed all in dusty grey, carrying a mask and a sign that said “Mr. Stark, I don’t feel so good.”) 
I lowkey made a couple people cry with it, actually, and I loved it 

And now I’m going to go over to my best friend’s house (it’s her birthday today) and we’re gonna go to the local Haunted Mine and I’ve changed my outfit/costume so now I’ve become 

Bitten by a radioactive lesbian

I’m so pumped. I think it’s hilarious. 

Idk, I might post a pic later

Either way I’m too pumped up on Halloween to contain myself so I just had to post about it

summary: how to introduce cindy moon in mcu (is this becoming a series? idk): a few years before homecoming, the shield agent jessica...
body:
how to introduce cindy moon in mcu (is this becoming a series? idk): a few years before homecoming, the shield agent jessica drew had the mission to find cindy moon, who was 13 years in a bunker. shield gave cindy a new identity in midtown tech and advised her not to search for her family, because their enemies could find her.

jess is a maternal figure to cindy, helping her to investigate on ezekiel, the man who locked her in the bunker, the spider who bite her and her family, along with anya corazon, the araña. cindy gets a job as a reporter on the daily bugle. she takes on the secret identity of silk, to fight a new villain, who is later revealed to be ezekiel.

at the end of the movie, cindy defeats ezekiel and finds her family.

for cindy i suggest:

IU

or

tiffany espensen

for jess i sugest

stephanie beatriz

for anya i suggest

victoria moroles

caption:
hALLOWEEN

This is my first time in years that I’ve gone out in a non subtle costume, since anxiety doesn’t help me much.

It ended up being nice tho. Some dude sang the Spider-man theme HSGDHS

The colors got hecked, but there is a logo on that hoodie. Originally we were gonna cut the sleeves to match Scarlet Spider’s hoodie, but I ended up getting attached to it so…no cutting

In the future I hope to figure out how to make the eyes completely white from an outside perspective!

Peter jerked up in his seat, wide eyes scanning the room quickly. His gaze landed on Mr Stark’s...
body:
«Mr Parker? Are you with us?»

Peter jerked up in his seat, wide eyes scanning the room quickly. His gaze landed on Mr Stark’s dark eyes. And he did not look pleased.

«Y-yes, I am, Mr Stark.» Peter blurted out the lie, picking up his pen and scribbling something in his notebook quickly as his classmates laughed at him. However, the older man did not fall for it and tutted.

«Hmm, I don’t think you are. Come to my office after class.»

🍎🍎🍎

«Is that a new belt, Sir? I think it looks great on you.»

«Oh no, you can’t get out of this by flattering me, boy. But since you like my belt so much, perhaps I will spank you with it instead of using my hand? Come on, Pete boy, drop your pants and bend over.»

«Yes, Sir.»

«Excuse me?»

«Yes, Daddy…»

«That’s better.»

summary: how to introduce gwen stacy in the mcu: a new student appears in midtown, gwen stacy. in this version, gwen looks like her...
body:
how to introduce gwen stacy in the mcu: a new student appears in midtown, gwen stacy. in this version, gwen looks like her counterpart in into the spiderverse, with shaved hair and piercings. at the same time, a white-hooded spider-powered vigilante who has been sabotaging oscorp’s laboratories. j. jonah jameson names her the ghost spider. at first, peter has an antagonistic relashionship with her. later in the movie, it’s revealed that gwen is the spider vigilante, with MJ acting as her ‘girl in the chair’. MJ already knows about peter’s identity and revealed it to gwen.

at the end of the movie, peter is pushed from the oscorp building by the main villain of the movie, the green goblin, and gwen saves him, like in the scene of the amazing spiderman 2.

for gwen i have three picks:

madison iseman

or

elle fanning

or

lana condor

(if there’s any spelling error, it’s because i’m brazilian)
